l be a tough battle, don't go diving in! Before you start, pick the most handy weapons with powerful ammunition. Remember strengthen your defensive equipment, and be prepared for anything.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592670/extras/892d6aeb5e8753c4b5968bf8053b6f61.webp?t=1695347944\" width=604 height=12 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592670/extras/57e0159bc371b899b30375e1256bdb90.poster.avif?t=1695347944\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592670/extras/57e0159bc371b899b30375e1256bdb90.webm?t=1695347944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592670/extras/57e0159bc371b899b30375e1256bdb90.mp4?t=1695347944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get blown up? It's okay, the battlefield will be reset for you in the next second! Enjoy the thrill of fighting with fast retries! Get stronger and stronger in infinite rebirth!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592670/extras/892d6aeb5e8753c4b5968bf8053b6f61.webp?t=1695347944\" width=604 height=12 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592670/extras/2dc6c4e0cd61aff5fdf0609c6d72e272.poster.avif?t=1695347944\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592670/extras/2dc6c4e0cd61aff5fdf0609c6d72e272.webm?t=1695347944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592670/extras/2dc6c